        "created_at": "2016-11-16T10:26:12.000Z",
        "cooked": "<ul>\n<li>\n<a href=\"http://www.cellartracker.com/wine.asp?iWine=230173\"><strong>1993 Domaine Ch\u00e2teau De La Tour Clos Vougeot</strong></a> <em>- France, Burgundy, C\u00f4te de Nuits, Clos Vougeot Grand Cru (11/16/2016)</em><br>\nVery savoury and very good. It smells of damp earth, pine needle sap, tar, leather and moss. In the mouth it is rich and powerful with plenty of meat and earth and flavours that are strewn with iron filings. There\u2019s some brown spices and a suggestion of camphor. It is dense with plenty of chew. You get a tart cherry snap on the finish.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Posted from <a href=\"http://www.cellartracker.com\">CellarTracker</a></em></p>",
