        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/jcoley3/{size}/507_2.png",
        "created_at": "2016-11-17T04:04:05.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>They were an Accad client in the 80s, IIRC.</p>\n<p>I had a 1961 Chevalier de Tastevinage selection from here that is a top five wine of my life. One of those wines I remember like it was yesterday, and it was 10 years ago.</p>",
